originalText.text: Dr. Marn is simply the best! She has taken care of our kids for the last 5 years and has been wonderful. They even look forward to her visits (and the toys she gives them:) A few weeks ago, our kid had an urgent visit where he got hurt doing sports and his teeth were loose:( Dr Marn saw us right away and took good care of us with X-rays and good follow up care (even calling us to make sure everything was ok)… I can’t explain fully in this review how much we trust and love Dr. Marn. Highly recommend her!!!

originalText.text: Dr. Marn is a great dentist! Going to the dentist is such a fun event for my children due to Dr. Marn and staff. My family absolutely trust Dr. Marn in her care and attention. Added bonus, we never have to wait long for an appointment!
